      <title>超微确认将推迟年度财务报告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/super-micro-confirms-it-will-delay-annual-financial-filings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[超微计算机公司 (Super Micro Computer Inc.) 表示，在特别董事会委员会审查内部控制期间，公司将不会提交年度财务报告，这证实了本周早些时候的一份声明，该声明导致其股价出现近六年来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/super-micro-confirms-it-will-delay-annual-financial-filings</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 20:55:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rhodium 获得罕见的基于比特币的破产贷款批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/rhodium-gets-approval-for-rare-bitcoin-based-bankruptcy-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[破产的加密矿工 Rhodium Encore LLC 周五获得法院批准，可进行一项不寻常的债务​​人持有融资计划，该计划提供以美元或比特币借款的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/rhodium-gets-approval-for-rare-bitcoin-based-bankruptcy-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 20:13:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆迪将电信巨头 BCE 的评级下调至仅比垃圾级高一级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/telecom-giant-bce-cut-to-one-notch-above-junk-by-moody-s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心这家电信公司的盈利增长无法跟上其债务负担，穆迪评级将 BCE Inc. 的评级降至垃圾级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/telecom-giant-bce-cut-to-one-notch-above-junk-by-moody-s</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 19:58:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克挑战最高法院命令，巴西法官禁止 X</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/judge-bans-x-in-brazil-after-musk-refuses-to-name-representative</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在社交网络巨头谷歌 X 的亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 违抗命令，没有在拉丁美洲最大的国家任命该社交网络的法律代表后，巴西最高法院下令立即暂停谷歌 X 在巴西的服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/judge-bans-x-in-brazil-after-musk-refuses-to-name-representative</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 19:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
